sequenceDiagram
    participant DF as Data Fetching
    participant DG as Data Grouping
    participant GTG as Ground Truth Generation
    participant Review as Data Review & Validation
    participant DQ as Data Querying

    DF->>DF: Use Copilot to extract Q/A from DDQs
    DF->>DG: Pass raw Q/A data
    DG->>DG: Group similar data using MS Copilot
    DG->>GTG: Pass grouped data
    GTG->>GTG: Generate LLM-friendly reference via internal LLM script
    GTG->>Review: Pass ground truth
    Review->>Review: Automated/internal review and validation
    loop If issues found
        Review-->>DF: Feedback for re-fetch/group/gen
    end
    Review->>DQ: Pass validated ground truth
    DQ->>DQ: Access and query via custom chatbot in Word/Excel